### Variables Globales
@gatewayUrl = http://localhost:8080
@inventoryUrl = http://localhost:8082
@authUrl = http://localhost:8083
@orderUrl = http://localhost:8085

### ===================================================
### 1. AUTENTICACIÓN (AUTH SERVICE)
### ===================================================

### Login como Admin -> Copiar el token JWT e ingresar en la variable @token de abajo
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

###

### Login como User
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "user",
  "password": "user123"
}

###

